N2  - The topic, ?A Management Information System?What It is and Why? was suggested by work that I did recently in preparation for the German symposium, ?MIS?A Challenge to Scientific Research.? In reviewing my own ideas about management information, I keep coming back to one primary thought, that the only value that information has to management is to allow better decisions to be made.
